---
title: American Spiced Pork Steaks with Roast Veggie & Baby Spinach Medley
description: Sweet and mild All-American spices add a ton of flavour to these pork steaks. Combined with a colourful roast veggie mixture tossed with baby spinach, and a delicate smokey aioli on the side, this is a modern and delicious combination that will delight the family.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d54f01f162d6f001738aefd-1e54e995.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/american-spiced-pork-steaks-5d54f01f162d6f001738aefd-cb74ec79.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
